  "Description": {
    "English": "Vital launch and landing gear system.<br> <br>User is advised that specialised, Deuterium-derived fuel is required to recharge thruster. Launch procedures require sufficient fuel levels before activation.<br> <br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> to take off from planet.<br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "极为重要的起飞与降落系统。<br> <br>用户需知，推进器以专用的二氢衍生燃料充能，有了足够的燃料等级，才能起飞。<br> <br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span>，从星球上起飞。<br>在飞行时按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>，启动加速。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "重要的起飛與降落輪組系統。<br><br>建議使用二氫製的特殊燃料補充推進器。發射程序啟動前需有充足燃料。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> 自星球起飛。<br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> 啟動飛行中加速。",
    "USEnglish": "Vital launch and landing gear system.<br> <br>User is advised that specialized, Deuterium-derived fuel is required to recharge thruster. Launch procedures require sufficient fuel levels before activation.<br> <br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> to take off from planet.<br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost."
  },
